        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion and carrot are softening, dissolve your<strong> beef stock mix </strong>and<strong> soy sauce </strong>in 400ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[520ml]</span> [700ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>- this is your <strong>beef stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
