    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and <strong>beef stock </strong>and cook for 25-30 min, stirring frequently, until all of the stock has been absorbed, the rice is cooked and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>risotto bolognese</strong></p>",
