      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> risotto bolognese</strong> topped with the <strong>garlic & parsley croutons</strong> and the <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> remaining chopped parsley</strong> and <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
